Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[CLUB NAME]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally found it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the homepage of that girl's circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? There's no page of their works!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this site even trying?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.86,0:00:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a limit to blasphemy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They have no idea how amazing and precious this girl is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show each of you my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanging out with you today was really fun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? That's good
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama-chan, you joined a good club
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The senior members are nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,to be honest, I was worried at fist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like my papa, Yumine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel praised
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the manga you lended me.  It was really interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Tell me what you thought of it later
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to visit my club before class
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, got it.  Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumine has been my friend since elementary school
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.82,0:03:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We parted ways in middle school, but now we're reunited
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,, To me, she's a special friend
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Lyrics?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.80,0:03:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm.  We've left the lyrics to others until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Teru-senpai asked me to make a song ??? revisit (japanese includes vocals)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,, Knowing you, it'll be done in a flash
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.42,0:03:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had much inspiration yet (ahhh, konkai mada ii denpa orite kite nai na)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave this one to you (jikai saku mo tanomu yo)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,ima iroiro kouso netteru tokoro dakara
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kagiri aru, jikan no naka de
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think of you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata no kokoro wo ugokasu chikara wo watashi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.16,0:03:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? A breakthrough?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.06,0:03:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,For the first time in a while, I read a lot of manga yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a tenderly written masterpiece about a hidden awakening of love. himeteru setsunai koigokoru komayaka ni egaita kessaku to iu ka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,, Huh? Fujikawa-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You were everything to me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it's my fate to disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I loved you forever
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Yahoo, Honda-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, just now was...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wrote a poem to my Senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,, To your Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're someone special to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's clumsy, I want to put my best into it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Those feelings will surely reach them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Oh, why don't you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Help you? Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Once we're done, I have to work on the next one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand your feelings! Who do you mean by next? 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who? Um....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Seki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:04:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Forbidden love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.24,0:04:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, just your partner's a girl, 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be rumors ??? perhaps kamawazu? ato_____???
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Anyways, can you come to my classroom during lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to root for Fujikawa-senpai's love poem
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't have any experience, but I'll do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hear your idea of first love in detail,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,like how you love your papa
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I love my papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That would turn out absurd! It would turn out complicated!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,dorodoro de yayakoshikute sukuwarenai youna enshutsu shita hou impakuto ga aru kamo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You thieving cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.58,0:05:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What could Tama-chan have been doing earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a letter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you fallen in love? Doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sharp
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujikawa-senpai's gotten into a messy love affair and I'm helping her out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,, You can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too close to my Fujikawa-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You've really helped me Honda-chan! Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That blonde!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujikawa-san, you attitude towards making songs is so serious, I'm jealous
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I think of my songs as my children
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have as much resolve as you, Fujikawa-san
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Resolve, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, you could say I'm in love
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.02,0:06:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's difficult, I could devote my life to them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,However, making a a living in the indie world isn't that easy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,mm pro ni naru ka dou ka oitoite ongaku ni mukau shisei no hanashi to iu koto de
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,hitobanjuu kangae matomaranakute nemurenai to ka yoku aru shi ne
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujikawa-san, aren't you overplanning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep is important, and if you ruin your body you'll lose everything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to keep a level head and look at the bigger picture
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.06,0:07:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, don't worry! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujikawa-senpai is the passionate type, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the President is calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're both great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for keeping you waiting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.78,0:07:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we talk in the digital music club's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, come in
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I guess we'll be working in here
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,making our baby
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No... in a place like this... I... but I'm a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now now, sit down 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What does gender have to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the scenario Senpai gave me had a situation like this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inside a small cage 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think of you ... ???
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,, What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you putting me up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.10,0:08:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,???
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Any question?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making it with senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,that... baby
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, that's right.  Since we're making them for Senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,izure wa senpai noto koto ni naru ka mo
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, where was that scenario...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.76,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,katei kankei no fukuzatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there'll be all kinds of trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You think a messy relationship is better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Murakami scolded me for that kind of thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:08:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,  telling me to be level-headed
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that normal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, let's get started
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.51,0:09:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,???
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,O-ow, sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.86,0:09:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tama-chan, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, I think there was a misunderstanding
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.24,0:09:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,, A misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,, Fujikawa-senpai was talking about scenarios earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,, That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:10:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She thinks of her songs as her children
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That must have been what she meant
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Children?  What about children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fujikawa-senpai said she wanted to make children with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.28,0:10:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and I got flustered
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault, Senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,for playing with my feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are your feelings the only thing you want me to play with?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,watashi wa tomodachi wo nante ??? nante mousou shiteru no
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,???
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.55,0:10:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu-Yumine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,???
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be your ally, Tama-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we resolved our misunderstandings and were relieved
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:11:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,, But the fact that Yumine was looking out for me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,makes me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I think about it, when I first started making games
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yumine was the trigger
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,???
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first thought of joining the SNS club,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to make games myself???
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, today for Honda Tamaki-san
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Honda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.75,0:11:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please pay attention
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Please deliver this printout
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.20,0:11:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you weren't listening after all
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuda-san's house. She lives in your neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuda... Yumine-san
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:12:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,kyou ninshoku nan desu ... ???
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Honda-chan!
